  "instructions": [
    "In a small bowl, mix together yuzu-kosho, ferment-jang, and 2 tablespoons of butter.",
    "In a large saucepan, combine sliced carrots, potatoes, and onions.",
    "Add 1 cup of water to the saucepan and bring to a boil over high heat.",
    "Reduce heat to medium-low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Add the mixed yuzu-kosho and ferment-jang to the saucepan and stir to combine.",
    "Add the chopped kale to the saucepan and stir to combine.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve the stamppot hot, topped with the remaining 2 tablespoons of melted butter."
